<div class="uvIdeaHeader">
  <h2 class="uvIdeaTitle ">
    <a href="/forums/925735-aeries-ideas/suggestions/41223331-security-when-changing-a-username-in-ugn-also-u">
      
        Security - When Changing a Username in UGN, Also Update the Username in USO and USR
    </a>
  </h2>
    <div class="uvIdeaDescription uvIdeaDescription-truncated">
      
        <div class="typeset"><p>When changing a username, this change does not automatically cascade to the USR and USO tables causing school access having to be reassigned, and user preferences to not follow the user. This is an issue when name changes and in turn the username needs to change.</p>
</div>
    </div>
  
</div>


