  <h2 class="uvIdeaTitle ">
    <a href="/forums/925735-aeries-ideas/suggestions/42398809-security-show-inherited-permissions">
      
        Security - Show Inherited Permissions
    </a>
  </h2>
    <div class="uvIdeaDescription uvIdeaDescription-truncated">
      
        <div class="typeset"><p>If a security group has inherited permissions, it would be really helpful to have those indicated on that group screen so we&#39;ll know if we need to add or deny permission. Maybe a highlighted yellow box to show it&#39;s already been checked via inheritance?</p>
</div>
    </div>
  
