<li class="uvListItem uvIdea uvIdea-list">

<div class="uvIdeaHeader">
  <h2 class="uvIdeaTitle ">
    <a href="/forums/925735-aeries-ideas/suggestions/40577398-grade-submission-extend-grading-windows-for-a-si">
      
        Grade Submission - Extend Grading windows for a single teacher
    </a>
  </h2>
    <div class="uvIdeaDescription uvIdeaDescription-truncated">
      
        <div class="typeset"><p>There are many instances where a teacher needs to:<br>
-- Edit a report card after grading window<br>
-- Forgot to submit grades for their class</p>

<p>We would like a feature to allow offices to grant a single teacher a custom grade submission window to:</p>

<p>-- Update a single student&#39;s grade<br>
-- Update a period of grades <br>
-- Update all of their students grades</p>

<p>This would eliminate the tasks of the office / District to re-open the window for all teachers / transcribe paperwork, while providing the flexibility for normal circumstances.</p>
</div>
    </div>
  
</div>


<div class="uvIdeaVoteBadge">
    <div class="uvIdeaVoteCount" data-id="40577398">
      <strong>15</strong>
      <span> votes</span>
    </div>
  


