<div class="uvIdeaHeader">
  <h2 class="uvIdeaTitle ">
    <a href="/forums/925735-aeries-ideas/suggestions/41468170-do-not-allow-historical-records-to-be-edited-sec">
      
        Do not allow historical records to be edited - Security Enhancement
    </a>
  </h2>
    <div class="uvIdeaDescription uvIdeaDescription-truncated">
      
        <div class="typeset"><p>For historical information such as CNF and ADS, it would be nice to prevent changing records that were originally created in a prior year while logged into the current year. So in 2020, although I can scroll down and see CNF or ADS entries from 2019, 2018, etc., I would not be able to modify or delete them (based on date).</p>
</div>
    </div>
  
</div>


