<li class="uvListItem uvIdea uvIdea-list">

<div class="uvIdeaHeader">
  <h2 class="uvIdeaTitle ">
    <a href="/forums/925735-aeries-ideas/suggestions/40627780-add-more-granular-control-to-the-reset-parent-stud">
      
        Add more granular control to the Reset Parent/Student Accounts function
    </a>
  </h2>
    <div class="uvIdeaDescription uvIdeaDescription-truncated">
      
        <div class="typeset"><p>We would like the ability to limit which Parent/Student accounts would be affected by the Reset Parent/Student Accounts function.</p>

<p>Currently, the options are all Students, all Parents, or both.</p>

<p>Adding the ability to filter by grade/class/school, use Keep queries, and filter by active/inactive related student records would all be very helpful tools.</p>
</div>
    </div>
  
</div>


<div class="uvIdeaVoteBadge">
